LedgerForm is a Form
    is primary
    propagate as a drill
    title is "Ledger"
    Layout
        paragraph
            FinanceEnterpriseGroup
            FinanceEnterpriseGroup.EnterpriseGroup.Description
                no label
                display as text
        paragraph
            Ledger
            Description
                no label
        single column
            visible when (FinanceEnterpriseGroup.EnableRelatedPartyElimination)
                visible when (not CloseLedger)
                    EliminationLedger
        visible when (UserDefinedLedger)
            single column
                Active
            two column
                effective date
                has future changes
                    label is "FutureChanges"
